      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though you will find minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014standard wear that doesn't detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and the dual-zone climate control blows ice-cold. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium sound system, works perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, showing no signs of leaks or deferred maintenance. The car has been serviced regularly with synthetic oil, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. It drives straight, brakes firmly without pulsation, and offers a smooth, quiet ride. This is an honest, solid car that has been cared for and is ready for its next chapter.",
